---
title: Figgy Serrano Ham Panzanella Salad with Thyme Roasted Potatoes and Homemade Croutons
description: Al fresco season is upon us at last! For a summery indulgence in the evenings, enjoy this Figgy Serrano Ham Panzanella Salad. Definitely not your ordinary salad, it's full of fresh flavours inspired by Italy.
